TASK_DESCRIPTION=Remove all manual /compact logic from the Doey product. No role should ever send /compact to another pane — Claude Code has built-in auto-compact that handles this reliably. Manual attempts via send-keys are unreliable (feedback dialogs block, messages queue, context barely reduces). Scope: (1) Delete /doey-taskmaster-compact skill entirely, (2) Remove compact-related instructions from agent templates (doey-boss, doey-taskmaster, doey-subtaskmaster), (3) Remove compact references from any skills that mention it, (4) Remove compact from CLAUDE.md if referenced.
